<pre>Many thanks for your letter of
Jan. 23. Dr. S t r e b e l has applied for
a Swiss stipendium, which will enable him to
go to America.  We have the impression that
this will be granted.  If not, he could per-
haps apply for 1954/55.  In any case I keep
the application forms you sent me.</pre>
      <div class="closing">Yours most cordially</div>
    </div>
